hadiths[74]{hadithnumber,text}:
2016,"Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ko Talaq di, phir ruju farma liya."
2017,"Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : logon ko kya ho gaya hai ke Allah ki hudood (aur uskey qanoon) ko khel bana letey hain. aadmi (apni biwi sey) kehta hai : mainey tujhey Talaq di, mainey tujh sey ruju kiya, mainey tujhey Talaq di."
2018,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : halal kamon mein sey Allah ko sab sey ziyada na pasand kaam, Talaq hai."
2019,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey apni aurat ko Talaq di jabke wo haiz ke dinon mein thi. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney ye baat Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko batai to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : usey hukm do ke us sey ruju kar ley (aur usey Talaq na dey) yahan tak key wo (haiz sey) pak ho jaey, phir usey haiz aaye, phir wo pak ho, phir agar chahey to us sey hum bistar honey sey pehley Talaq dey aur chahey to usey (nikah mein) rok ley. ye wo iddat hai jis ka Allah ney hukm diya hai."
2020,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Talaaqe sunnat ye hai ke aurat ko tuhur (paaki) ki haalat mein aur jima (sambhog) kiye baghair Talaq dey."
2021,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney masnoon Talaq key barey mein farmaya : aurat ko har tuhur (paaki) main eik Talaq dey, jab teesri baar tuhur (paaki) aa ley to usey (aakhiri) Talaq dey dey, iskey baad wo eik haiz iddat guzaarey."
2022,"Hazrat Abu-Ghilaab Yunus bin Juber Baahli (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : mainey Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey puchha ke agar mard apni aurat ko haiz ke dinon mein Talaq dey dey (to kya hukm hai)? unhoney kaha : aap Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) ko jantey hain? usney apni biwi ko Talaq dey di thi jabke wo dinon mein thi (main tumhen apna waqia sunata hun). phir Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar maamla arz kiya to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney ruju kar leney ka hukm diya. mainey kaha : wo Talaq shumar hogi ? unhoney farmaya : agar wo aajiz ho ya himaqat karey to?"
2023,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke unhoney apni biwi ko haiz ke dinon mein Talaq dey di . Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney ye baat Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko batai to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : usey hukm do ke ruju kar ley, phir usey us waqt Talaq dey jab wo pak ho ( tuhur ke dinon mein ho) ya hamila ho."
2024,"Hazrat Aamir Shaabey (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Hazrat Fatima binte Qais (Raziallahu anha) sey kaha : mujhey apni Talaq key barey mein bataaiye. unhoney farmaya : merey khawind ney mujhey teen talaaqein dey den jabke wo Yamen gaey huye they to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney usey nafiz (laagu) qarar dey diya."
2025,Hazrat Mutrif bin Abdullah bin Shikhkhir (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anha) sey sawal kiya gaya ke eik aadmi apni biwi ko Talaq deta hai aur phir us sey mubashrat (sambhog) karta hai magar Talaq deney ya us sey ruju karney par gawah nahin banata (uska kya hukm hai)?  Hazrat Imran (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : tu ney sunnat key khilaf Talaq di aur sunnat key khilaf hi ruju kiya. uski Talaq par bhi gawah muqarrar kar aur ruju par bhi.
2026,"Hazrat Zuber bin Awam (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Hazrat Umme Kulsoom binte Aqba (Raziallahu anha) unkey nikah mein thin. hamal ke dinon mein unhoney us (Zuber) sey kaha : eik Talaq dey kar mera dil khush kar dijiye. unhoney eik Talaq dey di. iskey baad wo namaz key liye chaley gaey, wapis aaye to Umme kulsoom (Raziallahu anha) key yahan wiladat ho chuki thi. unhoney kaha : usney ye kyon kiya? usney mujh sey dhoka kiya hai. Allah usey dhokey ki saza dey, phir wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huye (aur waqia bayan kiya) to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah key qanoon key mutabiq muqarrar waqt guzar chuka. (ab (usey) dobara) nikah ka pegham dey do."
2027,"Hazrat Abu-Sanaabil (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Hazrat Sabeeaa binte Haris Aslamiya (Raziallahu anha) key yahan , unkey khawind ki wafat sey bees din sey chand din baad wiladat ho gaee. jab wo nifaas sey farigh huin to unhoney nikah ka irada zahir kiya, is par logon ney tanqeed ki. aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key samney bhi unkey is kaam ka zikr huwa to aap ney farmaya : agar wo aisa karti hai to (jayez hai kyonkey) uski iddat guzar chuki hai."
2028,"Hazrat Masruq aur Hazrat Amr bin Utba (Rahimahullah)  sey riwayat hai ke un dono ney Hazrat Sabeeaa binte Haris (Raziallahu anha) ko khat likh kar unka waqia daryaft kiya to unhoney (jawab mein) un hazraat ko likha ke unkey yahan, unkey khawind ki wafat sey pachchees din baad wiladat ho gaee, chunanche unhoney achchhey kaam (nikah) key iradey sey tayyari ki. Hazrat Abu-Sanaabil bin Ba'kak (Raziallahu anhu) unkey paas sey guzrey to farmaya : tum ney jaldi ki, baad wali muddat , yani chaar maah das din mukammal honey tak iddat guzaaro. (wo farmaati hain : ) mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar arz ki : Allah key Rasool ! merey liye maghfirat ki dua kijiye. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : wo kyon? mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko waqiey sey aagah kiya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : agar tumhen nek khawind mil jaey to nikah kar lo."
2029,Hazrat Miswar bin Makhrima (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Sabeeaa (Raziallahu anha) ko nifaas sey farigh honey par nikah kar leney ka hukm diya.
2030,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : qism hai Allah ki ! jo shakhs chahey hum us sey mubaahala kar (eik doosre ko laanat karna) saktey hain ke aurton key masaayel ki chhoti sura (Sura- Talaaq) chaar maah das din ka hukm nazil honey key baad nazil hui thi."
2031,"Hazrat Zenab binte Kaab bin Ajra (Raziallahu anha) jo Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ki zauja (biwi) mohtarma thin, Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ki behan Hazrat Fariaa binte Malik (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat karti hain, unhoney farmaya : merey shohar apney kuchh (bhagey huye) ghulamon ki talash mein nikley. (aakhir) ""qudoom"" jagah key qarib unhen ja liya. ghulamon ney unhen shaheed kar diya. jab mujhey merey khawind ki wafat ki khabar mili to main apney khandan key mohalley sey door ansaar key eik makaan mein rihaaish pazeer (reh rahi) thi. main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui aur kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! mujhey khawind ki wafat ki khabar is haal mein mili hai ke main eik aisey makaan mein reh rahi hun jo merey khandan key mohalley sey bhi door hai aur merey bhaiyon key gharon sey bhi door hai. aur usney koi maal bhi nahin chhoda jis sey mera kharch chalta rahey, na koi maal chhoda hai jo mujhey tarkey mein miley, na un ki milkiyat mein koi ghar tha. agar aap munasib samjhen to mujhey ijazat dey den ke main apney aqaarib aur apney bhaiyon key ghar chali jaun. mujhey ye baat ziyada pasand hai aur is sey merey (roz marra key) kaam behtar tor par chaltey rahengey. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : agar tum chaho to yun hi kar lo. wo farmaati hain : main bahar nikli to mujhey is baat ki khushi thi ke Allah ney apney Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki zaban sey merey haq mein faisla farmaya. main abhi masjid hi mein thi ya ghar key sehan hi mein thi ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney mujhey (dobara) talab farma liya, phir farmaya : tum ney kaisey bayan kiya? mainey dobara soorate haal pesh ki. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tak Allah ki muqarrar karda muddat (maut ki iddat) puri nahin ho jati, usi ghar mein rihaaish rakho jahan tumhen apney khawind ki wafat ki khabar pahunchi. chunanche mainey chaar maah das din tak wahin iddat guzaari."
2032,"Hazrat Urwa bin Zuber (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main Marwan key paas gaya aur un sey kaha : aap key khandan ki eik aurat ko Talaq ho gaee hai. mera guzar uskey yahaan sey huwa to dekha ke wo (kisi aur ghar mein) muntaqil ho rahi hai. wo kehti hai : hamein Hazrat Fatima bint Qais (Raziallahu anha) ney muntaqil honey ko kaha hai aur bataya hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney unhen (Fatima binte Qais (Raziallahu anha) ko) rihaaish tabdeel kar leney ka hukm diya tha. Marwan ney kaha : unhon (Fatima) ney hi unhen aisa karney ko kaha hai. Urwa (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke mainey kaha : qism hai Allah ki ! Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ney is par tanqeed ki thi aur kaha tha ke Fatima eik wiran ghar mein thin aur unhen khatra tha (ke akeli paa kar koi bura chahney wala nuqsan pahunchaney ki koshish na karey) isliye Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney unhen ijazat di thi."
2033,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya ke Hazrat Fatima binte Qais (Raziallahu anha) ney arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! mujhey dar lagta hai ke koi merey ghar mein na ghus aaye to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney unhen muntaqil ho janey ka hukm dey diya."
2034,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : meri khaala ko Talaq ho gaee. unhoney apney khajuron key darakhton ka phal utaarna chaha. eik aadmi ney unhen ghar sey nikal kar (baagh mein) janey sey mana kiya to wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huin (aur masla poochha). aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : haan ! apni khajuron ka phal utaar lo, shayad tum sadqa karo ya koi neki ka kaam karo."
2035,Hazrat Fatima binte Qais (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke unkey khawind ney unhen teen talaaqein dey den to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney unhen rihaaish aur kharch na dlwaya.
2036,"Hazrat Fatima binte Qais (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya ke mujhey merey khawind ney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key zamaney mein teen talaaqein dey den to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : terey liye na rihaaish hai na kharch."
2037,Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Umra binte Joon‬ (Raziallahu anha) ko jab Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein pesh kiya gaya (jab un ki rukhsati hui) to unhoney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey Allah ki panah maangi (ye kaha : aap sey Allah bachaey). Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tu ney uski panah li hai jiski panah li jati hai. chunanche aap ney isey Talaq dey di. aur Hazrat Usama (Raziallahu anhu) ya Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ko hukm diya to unhoney usey teen safed sooti kapdey dey diye.
2038,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab aurat khawind sey Talaq mil janey ka daawey karey aur eik qabile-aitimaad gawah pesh kar dey to uskey khawind sey qism uthaney ka mutalba kiya jaeyga. agar usney qism kha li (ke mainey Talaq nahin di) to gawah ki gawahi raddh ho jaeygi. aur agar usney qism sey inkar kiya to uska inkar doosrey gawah key qaaim maqam ho jaeyga aur uski Talaq nafiz (laagu) kar di jaeygi."
2039,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : teen cheezen qasd (irada) aur iraday sey ki jaeyn to bhi haqeeqi (shumar hoti) hain aur hansi mazaq mein ki jaeyn to bhi haqeeqi (shumar hoti) hain : nikah, Talaq aur ruju."
2040,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah ney meri ummat key logon sey wo sab kuchh maaf kar diya hai jo wo apney dilon sey baat karen, jab tak us (khayal) ko amal mein na laeyn ya (zaban sey) kalam na karen."
2041,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : teen afrad sey qalam utha liya gaya hai : soey huye sey yahan tak key wo jaag padey, bachchey sey yahan tak key wo baligh ho jaey aur deewaney sey yahan tak key uski aql wapis aa jaey, ya usey (waqti taur par) ifaaqa (faayda) ho jaaey. eik riwayat mein hai : (zehni) bimari waley sey yahan tak key wo tandurust ho jaey."
2042,"Hazrat Ali bin Abu-Talib (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : bachchey sey , pagal sey aur soey huye sey qalam utha liya jata hai."
2043,"Hazrat Abu-Zar Ghifaari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah ney meri khatir meri ummat ko ghalati, bhool aur wo kaam maaf kar diye hain jin par unhen majbur kiya gaya ho."
2044,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala ney meri ummat key unkey dilon mein aaney waley waswasey maaf kar diye hain, jab tak un par amal na karen, ya unhen zaban sey ada na karen aur (wo gunah bhi maaf kar diye hain) jin par unhen zabardasti majbur kya jaey."
2045,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala ney meri ummat sey ghalati , bhool aur wo gunah maaf kar diye hain jin par unhen zabardasti majbur kiya gaya ho."
2046,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : zabardasti mein na Talaq hoti hai, na ghulam azad hota hai."
2047,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib ney apney walid sey , aur unhoney apney dada (Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhuma)) sey riwayat ki, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya is (aurat) ko Talaq nahin (di ja sakti) jo Talaq deney waley ki milkiyat (nikah mein) na ho."
2048,"Hazrat Miswar bin Makhrima (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : nikah sey pehley Talaq nahin aur Malik ban'ney sey pehley ghulam ka azad karna (durust) nahin."
2049,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : nikah sey pehley Talaq nahin."
2050,"Imam (Abdur-Rehman bin Amr) Auzaai (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Imam (Muhammad bin Muslim Shahab) Zohri (Rahimahullah) sey puchha ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki kis zauja (biwi) mohtarma ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey Allah ki panah maangi thi? unhoney kaha : mujhey Hazrat Urwa (Rahimahullah) ney Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat kartey huye bataya ke binte Joon (Raziallahu anha) jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key paas (khilwat mein) pahunchin to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) unkey qarib gaey, unhoney kaha : main aap sey Allah ki panah chahti hun to Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tu ney azeem hasti ki panah ley li, apney ghar walon key paas chali ja."
2051,"Hazrat Yazeed bin Rukana (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke unhoney apni biwi ko Talaqe-bitta (teen Talaq) dey di, phir unhoney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar masla daryaft kiya to Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : is (lafz) sey teri niyat kya thi? unhoney kaha : eik Talaq ki. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya Allah ki qism utha kar kehtey ho ke tumhari niyat eik hi Talaq ki thi? unhoney kaha : qism hai Allah ki ! meri niyat sirf eik Talaq ki thi. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney us khatoon ko dobara unkey sath rehney ki ijazat dey di (aur Sabab ko ruju karney ki ijazat dey di). Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) ney farmaya : mainey Abul-Hasan Ali bin Muhammad Tanaafusi ko farmatey huye suna : ye hadees kitni achchhi hai ! (kyonkey is sey wazeh taur par Sabit hota hai ke Talaqe bitta (teen Talaq) mein mard ki niyat par faisla hoga. agar mard ney eik Talaq ki niyat ki hogi to eik waqey hogi, agar teen ki niyat hogi to teeno waqey ho jaeyngi).  isi ke saath Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) ney farmaya : Abu-Ubaid ko Naajiya ney tark kiya hua qarar diya aur Imam Ahmed ney us sey riwayat karney ki jur'at nahin ki."
2052,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hamein ikhtiyar diya. hamney aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (ki zojiyat (nikah) mein rehney) ko muntakhab (ikhtiyar) kar liya. to aap ney isey (Talaq waghera) kuchh bhi shumar nahin kiya."
2053,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : jab Sura Ehzaab ki ye aayat nazil hui : (وَإِن كُنتُنَّ تُرِدْنَ ٱللَّهَ وَرَسُولَهُۥ),''agar tum Allah ki, uskey Rasool ki aur aakhirat key ghar ki Talib ho to Allah ney tum mein sey neki karney waaliyon key liye ajrr-azeem tayyar kar rakha hai.'' to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) merey paas tashrif laye aur farmaya : Aaisha ! main tujhey eik baat keh raha hun, behtar hai ke to is (ka faisla kerney) mein jaldi na karna balke apney waliden sey mashwara kar lena. Ummul-mominin ney kaha : Allah ki qism ! (aap ney mashwara leney ko isliye farmaya tha ke) aap ko yaqin tha ke merey waliden mujhey kabhi aap sey judai ka mashwara nahin dengey. Ummul-mominin (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain : (ye farmaney key baad) aap ney mujhey wo aayaat padh kar sunaee : (يَـٰٓأَيُّهَا ٱلنَّبِىُّ قُل لِّأَزْوَجِكَ إِن كُنتُنَّ تُرِدْنَ ٱلْحَيَوةَ ٱلدُّنْيَا وَزِينَتَهَا),''aey Nabi ! apni biwiyon sey farma dijiye ke agar tumhen duniya ki zindagi aur duniya ki zeb aur zeenat matloob hai to aao main tumhen kuchh maal dey kar achchhey tareeqey sey rukhsat kar dun. aur agar tum Allah ki, uskey Rasool ki aur aakhirat key ghar ki Talib ho to Allah ney tum mein sey neki karney waaliyon key liye ajre-azeem tayyar kar rakha hai.'' mainey kaha : (aey Allah key Rasool ! ) kya main is mamley mein apney waliden sey mashwara karun? mainey (duniya ki dolat key muqabley mein) Allah aur uskey Rasool (ki raza aur mohabbat) ka intikhaab (chunaaw) kar liya hai."
2054,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo aurat baghair kisi waaqe sabab key apney khawind sey Talaq maangeygi, usey jannat ki khushbu nahin aayegi, halanke uski khushbu chaalis saal key fasley sey mehsus hoti hai."
2055,"Hazrat Soban (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis aurat ney baghair sakht majburi key apney khawind sey Talaq maangi, is par jannat ki khushbu haram hai."
2056,Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Jameela binte Salool‬ (Raziallahu anha) ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar arz kiya : Allah ki qism ! main Sabit (bin Qais bin Shamaas) (Raziallahu anhu) key Deen aur akhlaq (ki kisi kharabi) ki wajeh sey naraz nahin lekin mujhey musalman hotey huye (khaawind ki) nashukri karna achchha nahin lagta. mujhey wo itney burey lagtey hain ke main unkey sath nahin reh sakti. to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney isey farmaya : kya tum usey uska baagh wapis dey do gi? unhoney kaha : ji haan. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) ko hukm diya ke un sey baagh wapis ley lein aur zayed kuchh na lein.
2057,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Hazrat Habiba binte Sehal (Raziallahu anha) Hazrat Sabit bin Qais bin Shamas (Raziallahu anhu) key nikah mein thin, aur wo khush shakal aadmi na they. Hazrat Habiba (Raziallahu anha) ney arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! qism hai Allah ki ! agar Allah ka dar na hota to jab wo merey paas aaye they, main unkey chehrey par thook deti. to Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya tum uska baagh wapis karti ho? unhoney kaha : ji haan. (hadees ke raawi ney kaha : ) chunanche unhoney unka baagh wapis kar diya aur Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney unkey darmiyan judai karwa di."
2058,"Hazrat Ubada bin Waleed (Rahimahullah) ney Hazrat Rabee binte Muawwiz bin Ifra Raziallahu anhum sey riwayat kartey huye farmaya ke mainey unhen kaha : mujhey apna waqia sunaaiye. unhoney farmaya : mainey apney khawind sey Khula ley liya, phir mainey Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar puchha : mujh par kitni iddat hai? unhoney farmaya : tum par koi iddat nahin, siwaye is surat key ke usney tujh sey thoda arsa pehley hambistari ki ho, tab tum uskey paas thahri raho yahan tak key eik haiz aa jaey. Hazrat Rabee (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ney us muqaddmey mein Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key us faisley ki perwi ki thi jo aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Maryam Maghaliyya‬ (Raziallahu anha) key barey mein diya tha. wo Hazrat Sabit bin Qais (Raziallahu anhu) key nikah mein thin, phir unhoney Khula ley liya tha."
2059,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney qism kha li ke aap eik mahina azwaje-mutahrat (paak biwiyon) Raziallahu anhu key paas tashrif nahin ley jaeyngey, chunanche aap untees din thehrey rahey. jab teeswen din ki Sham hui to aap merey yahaan tashrif ley aaye. mainey arz kiya : aap ney qism khai thi ke mahina bhar aap hamarey paas tashrif nahin laeyngey (aur abhi untees din purey huye hain, subah teeswaan din hoga). to aap ney teen baar ungliyon ka ishara kartey huye farmaya : mahina itna hota hai (tees din ka). aur (doosri baar) sari ungliyon sey (do baar ishara farma kar teesri baar eik ungli band ki, aur farmaya : aur mahina itna bhi hota hai) untees din ka."
2060,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney isliye elaa (alhedgi ikhtiyar) kiya tha ke Ummul-mominin Zenab (Raziallahu anha) ney aap ka bheja huwa hadiya wapis kar diya tha. (is par) Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ney kaha : Zenab (Raziallahu anha) ney aap ki azmat aur shaan ka khayal nahin kiya. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ghussa aa gaya aur aap ney un (sab) sey elaa (alhedgi ikhtiyar) kar liya ."
2061,Ummul-mominin Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney apni baaz azwaje-mutahrat (biwiyon) Raziallahu anhu sey eik mahiney key liye elaa (alhedgi ikhtiyar) kiya. jab untees din ho gaey to (teeswen din) Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) subah ya Sham key waqt (key paas) paak biwiyon ke paas tashrif ley gaey. arz kiya gaya : aey Allah key Rasool ! abhi untees din guzrey hain. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mahina untees din ka hai.
2062,"Hazrat Salma bin Sakhr Bayaazi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : mujhey aurton sey bahut raghbat (dilchaspi) thi. merey khayal mein koi mard itni kasrat sey sohbat nahin karta hoga jis kasrat sey main karta tha. jab Ramzan shuru huwa to mainey Ramzan khatam honey tak biwi sey zihar kar liya . eik raat wo mujh sey baaten kar rahi thi ke uskey jism ka kuch hissa khul gaya. main be qabu ho kar us sey hum bistar ho gaya . jab subh hui to mainey apni qom (key kuchh afrad) key paas ja kar apna waqia sunaya aur unhen kaha : mujhey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey (masla) poochh den (ke uska kaffara kya hai)? unhoney kaha : hum log to nahin poochhengey. (agar hamney puchha to) Allah Taala hamarey barey mein Quran Majeed (ki aayaat) nazil farma dega, ya Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) kuchh (narazi waley) alfaz irshad farma dengey jo hamarey liye aar ka baais baney rahen gey, isliye hum terey gunah key badley tujhi ko bhejtey hain. to khud hi ja kar Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein apna maamla arz kar. (Hazrat Salma (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain)  main rawana huwa yahan tak key aap ki khidmat mein hazir ho gaya aur apna waqia arz kiya to Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tu ney ye kaam kiya hai? mainey kaha : mainey ye kaam kiya hai aur aey Allah key Rasool ! main hazir hun. Allah ka merey barey mein jo hukm hoga, is par sabr (aur usey dil sey qubul) karta hun. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : eik gardan (ghulam ya londi) azad kar do. mainey kaha : qism hai us zaat ki jisney aap ko haq dey kar mab-us farmaya (bheja) hai ! main to sirf apni is gardan ka Malik hun. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tab musalsal do maah key rozey rakh lo. mainey arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! mujh par jo aazmaaish aai hai, ye bhi rozon hi ki wajeh sey aai hai. aap ney farmaya : tab sadqa kar. ya farmaya : saath miskinon ko khana khila. mainey kaha : qism hai us zaat ki jisney aap ko haq dey kar mab-us farmaya (Bheja) hai ! hamney to ye raat isi tarah guzaari hai ke hamarey paas Sham ka khana bhi nahin tha. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qabila banu zuraiq ki zakat jama karney waley aamil key paas ja, usey keh ke wo (apney qabiley ki) zakat tujhey dey dey. (us mein sey) saath miskinon ko khana khila dey aur baqi sey khud faeyda utha lena."
2063,"Hazrat Urwa bin Zuber (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha ke Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : Allah badi barkaton wala hai jo sab kuchh sunta hai. jab Hazrat Khaula binte Solba (Raziallahu anha) Rasul Allah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey apney khawind (Hazrat Aus bin Samit (Raziallahu anhu)) ki shikayat kar rahi thin to main bhi un ki baaten sun rahi thi lekin kuchh baaten (qarib honey key bawajood) meri samajh mein na aati thin . wo keh rahi thin : aey Allah key Rasool ! (mera khaawind) meri jawani kha gaya, mainey uskey liye (bachchey jann jann kar) pet khaali kar diya. ab jabke main boodhi ho gaee hun aur mujhey aulad hona band ho gaee hai to usney mujh sey zihar kar liya hai. ya Allah ! main tujhi sey shikayat karti hun. wo abhi wahin thin ke Jibreel (Alaihissalam) ye aayaat ley kar nazil ho gaey : (قَدْ سَمِعَ ٱللَّهُ قَوْلَ ٱلَّتِى تُجَـٰدِلُكَ فِى زَوْجِهَا وَتَشْتَكِىٓ إِلَى ٱللَّهِ),''yaqeenan Allah ney is aurat ki baat sun li jo tujh sey apney shohar key barey mein takraar kar rahi thi aur Allah key aagey shikayat kar rahi thi----."""
2064,"Hazrat Salma bin Sakhr Bayaazi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke zihar karney wala jo mard kaffara ada karney sey pehley mubashrat kar ley, uskey barey mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : (uskey zimmey) eik hi kaffara hai."
2065,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ney apni biwi sey zihar kiya, phir kaffara ada karney sey pehley us sey hum bistar ho gaya, phir usney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar waqia arz kiya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tu ney aisa kyon kiya? usney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! chaandni mein meri nazar uski paazebon par padi , phir mujhey apney aap par qabu na raha , aur main us sey mubashrat kar betha Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hans padey aur usey hukm diya ke kaffara ada karney sey pehley uskey qarib na jaey."
2066,"Hazrat Sehal bin Saad Saaid (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Uwemir (Raziallahu anhu) Hazrat Aasim bin Adi (Raziallahu anhu) key paas aaye aur kaha : mujhey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey ye baat poochh kar bataaiye ke agar koi shakhs apni biwi key sath kisi (ghair) mard ko (gunah mein mulawwis) dekhey aur (ghussey mein aa kar) usey qatl kar dey to kya usey (qisaas mein) qatl kiya jaeyga? warna wo kya kerey? Hazrat Aasim (Raziallahu anhu) ney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey ye (masla) daryaft kiya to Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney (is qism key) sawalat ko na-pasand farmaya. baad mein Hazrat Uwemir (Raziallahu anhu) Hazrat Aasim (Raziallahu anhu) sey miley to un sey daryaft kiya aur kaha : tum ney kya kiya? unhoney kaha : huwa ye hai ke tujh sey mujhey bhalai nahin pahunchi. mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey (masla)  daryaft kiya to aap ney sawalat ko na-pasand farmaya. Uwemir (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : Allah ki qism ! main zarur Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar ye baat poochhunga, chunanche wo Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huye to malum huwa ke aap par unkey barey mein wahi nazil ho chuki hai. aap ney un dono (miyan biwi) mein liaan  kara diya. Uwemir (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! agar ab main is aurat ko (ghar) ley jaun to (iska matlab hai ke) mainey is par jhoota ilzam lagaya hai, chunanche unhoney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key hukm deney sey pehley hi is aurat ko Talaq dey di, phir liaan karney walon mein yehi tariqa jari ho gaya. iskey baad Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : dekho ! agar us aurat key yahan siyah faam (rang), siyah aakhon wala, badey sirinon (peeth) wala bachcha paida huwa to merey khayal mein us (Uwemir (Raziallahu anhu)) ney yaqinan sach kaha hai. aur agar uskey yahaan bair bahuti jaisa surkh bachcha paida huwa to merey khayal mein us (Uwemir) ney zarur jhoot bola hai.  Raavi bayan kartey hain : phir us aurat key yahan buri surat wala bachcha paida huwa."
2067,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Hilal bin Umayya (Raziallahu anhu) ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar apni biwi par Shareek bin Sehma (Raziallahu anhu) sey mulawwis honey ka ilzam lagaya to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : gawah pesh karo, warna tumhari peeth par (qazaf ki) had lagey gi. Hazrat Hilal bin Umayya (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : qism hai us zaat ki jisney aap ko haq key sath mab-us farmaya (bheja) hai, main bilkul sachcha hun. aur Allah Taala merey mamley mein zarur (wahi) nazil farma dega jis sey meri peeth (had lagney sey) bach jaeygi. to Raavi farmatey hain ke tab ye aayaat nazil huin : (وَٱلَّذِينَ يَرْمُونَ أَزْوَجَهُمْ وَلَمْ يَكُن لَّهُمْ شُهَدَآءُ إِلَّآ أَنفُسُهُمْ . . . وَٱلْخَـٰمِسَةَ أَنَّ غَضَبَ ٱللَّهِ عَلَيْهَآ إِن كَانَ مِنَ ٱلصَّـٰدِقِينَ),''aur wo log jo apni biwiyon par tohmat lagatey hain aur unkey paas apney siwa koi gawah na hon to un mein sey eik ki shahadat is tarah hogi ke chaar baar Allah ki qism kha kar kahey ke beshak wo sachchon mein sey hai. aur paanchwin baar ye kahey ke agar wo jhooton mein sey ho to is par Allah ki lanat ho. aur aurat sey tab saza talti hai ke wo chaar baar Allah ki qism kha kar kahey ke bila-shubah wo (uska khawind ( jhooton mein sey hai aur paanchwen baar ye kahey ke agar wo (uska khaawind) sachchon mein sey ho to us (aurat) par Allah ka ghazab ho.'' Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) lotey to un dono ko bula bheja, wo aagey to Hilal bin Umayya (Raziallahu anhu) ney khadey ho kar gawahi di aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farma rahey they : Allah Taala ko malum hai ke tum mein sey eik jhoota hai to kya dono mein sey koi eik tauba karta hai? phir khatoon khadi hui aur usney gawahi di (aur qasmen khaaeen) jab wo paanchwin (gawahi) key waqt ye kehney lagi ke agar wo jhooti ho to is par Allah ka ghazab nazil ho. to haazirin ney isey kaha : ye qism (Allah key ghazab ko) wajib kar deney wali hai. Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) ney bayan farmaya : (ye sun kar) usney twaqquf kiya (thehri), aur peechhey hati yahan tak key hamein ye khayal paida huwa ke wo (be-gunah honey key dawey sey) ruju kar ley gi, phir usney kaha : qism hai Allah ki ! main apni qom ko hamesha key liye badnaam nahin karungi (aur paanchwin qism bhi kha li). to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya is (key yahan wiladat honey) ka intizar karo. agar usney surmain aakhon wala , badiy peeth wala, moti pindliyon wala bachcha jana to wo Shareek bin Sehma ka hoga. (waqt aaney par) uskey yahaan aisa hi bachcha paida huwa. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : agar Allah ki kitab ka hukm nazil na ho chuka hota to mera us aurat sey (doosra) maamla hota."
2068,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Jumey ki raat hum log masjid mein they ke eik aadmi ney kaha : agar koi mard apni biwi key sath kisi (ghair) mard ko (gunah ki haalat mein) dekh kar qatl kar dey to tum log usey (qisaas key tor par) qatl kar dogey. agar wo (apni biwi key mujrim honey ki) baat karey to tum usey (ilzam taraashi ki saza key tor par) kodey lagaogey. qism hai Allah ki ! main ye baat zaroor Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey arz karunga. aakhir kaar usney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey zikr kar diya to Allah Taala ney liaan ki aayat nazil farma den. uskey baad us aadmi ney aa kar apni biwi par ilzam lagaya to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney un dono (miyan biwi) key darmiyan liaan karwa diya. aur farmaya : shayad us aurat key yahan siyah faam (rang) bachcha paida ho.  chunanche siyah faam (rang) aur ghunghriyaaley baalon wala bachcha hi paida huwa."
2069,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke eik mard ney apni aurat sey liaan kiya aur uskey betey ko apna man'ney sey inkar kiya to Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney un dono key darmiyan judai kara di aur bachchey ko aurat key sath kar diya.
2070,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke eik Ansari aadmi ney qabila banu Ajlan ki eik aurat sey nikah kiya, chunanche usney us sey sohbat ki aur raat bhar uskey paas raha. jab subah hui to usney kaha : mainey isey baakara (kanwari) nahin paya. uska muqadma Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein pesh kiya gaya to aap ney ladki ko bula kar daryaft kiya to usney kaha : main to baakara (kanwari) thi , chunanche Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney un dono mein liaan karwaya aur ladki ko haq mehar dilwaya."
2071,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : chaar aurton sey liaan nahin kiya jata : musalman mard ki Esai biwi, musalman mard ki Yahudi biwi, ghulam khawind ki azad biwi aur azad khawind ki wo biwi jo (kisi aur ki) londi ho."
2072,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney apni biwiyon sey elaa kiya aur (un ko apney oopper)  haram kar liya, halal chiz ko haram kiya aur qism ka kaffara ada kiya."
2073,Hazrat Saeed bin Juber (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) ney halal chiz ko haram kar leney key barey mein farmaya : ye qism hai. aur Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) farmaya kartey they : ( لَّقَدْ كَانَ لَكُمْ فِى رَسُولِ ٱللَّهِ أُسْوَةٌ حَسَنَةٌ )''tumharey liye Allah key Rasool mein achchha namoona hai.''
2074,Ummul-mominin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke unhoney Hazrat Barira (Raziallahu anhuma) ko azad kiya to Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney unhen ikhtiyar dey diya aur unka khawind azad tha.
2075,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Hazrat Barira (Raziallahu anha) key shohar ghulam they. unhen Mughees (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey they. (mujhey wo manzar yad hai) goya main un (Mughees) ko dekh raha hun ke wo Barira (Raziallahu anha) key peechhey rotey phir rahey hain aur unkey rukhsaaron par aansu beh rahey hain to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey farmaya : aey Abbas ! kya aap ko tajjub nahin hota ke Mughees Barira sey (shadeed) mohabbat karta hai aur Barira (Raziallahu anha) Mughees (Raziallahu anhu) sey (shadeed) nafrat karti hai? (eik baar) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Barira (Raziallahu anha) sey farmaya : kaash! ! tum un sey ruju kar lo, aakhir wo tumharey bachchon key baap hain. unhoney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! aap mujhey hukm farma rahey hain? Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : main to sifarish karta hun. to unhoney kaha : mujhey un ki koi zarurat nahin."
2076,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Hazrat Barira (Raziallahu anha) ki wajeh sey teen sunnatein qaaim huin (aur teen sharae masaayel malum huye :)  (eik ye ke) jab wo azad huin to unhen ikhtiyar diya gaya . aur unka khawind ghulam tha. (doosri ye ke) log unhen sadqa detey they, wo (us sey kuchh) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko hadiya dey deti thin. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmatey they : ye is par sadqa hai, aur hamarey liye hadiya hai. (teesri ye ke) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : wala usi ka hai jo azad karey."
2077,Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Barira (Raziallahu anha) ko teen haiz iddat guzarney ka hukm diya gaya.
2078,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Barira (Raziallahu anha) ko ikhtiyar diya.
2079,"Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : londi ki talaaqein do hain, aur uski iddat do haiz hai."
2080,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : londi ki talaaqein do hain aur us (ki iddat) key haiz bhi do hain.  abu-Aasim (Rahimahullah) ney kaha : mainey is hadees ka Mazaahir sey zikr kiya aur kaha : aap mujh sey isi tarah hadees bayan karen jis tarah ibne-Jurej sey bayan ki hai, chunanche unhoney Qasim key wastey sey Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat bayan ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : londi ki do talaaqein hain aur uski iddat do haiz hai."
2081,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! merey aaqa ney apni londi sey mera nikah kar diya tha. ab wo usey mujh sey juda karna chahta hai. hadees ke raavi ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) ney kaha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) member par tashrif farma huye aur farmaya : logo ! kya wajeh hai ke koi shakhs apney ghulam sey apni londi ka nikah kar deta hai, phir un dono mein judai dalna chahta hai? Talaq dena to usi ka haq hai jisney pindli ko pakda."
2082,"Hazrat Abul-Hasan Mola banu Naufal (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey puchha gaya ke agar ghulam apni biwi ko (jo kisi ki londi ho) do talaaqein dey dey, phir wo dono azad ho jaeyn to kya wo us sey (dobara) nikah kar sakta hai? unhoney kaha : haan. un sey kaha gaya : (aap ye masla) kis sey (riwayat kartey hain)? unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney yehi faisla diya tha. Hazrat Abdullah bin Mubarak (Rahimahullah) ney farmaya : Abul-Hasan ney apni gardan par bahut badi chattan utha li hai."
2083,"Hazrat Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum par hamarey Nabi Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki sunnat khalat-malat na karo. Umme Walad ki iddat chaar mahiney das din hai."
2084,Ummul-mominin Hazrat Umme-Salma aur Ummul-mominin Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke eik aurat ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar arz kiya ke uski eik beti ka khawind faut ho gaya hai aur uski aankhen kharab ho gaee hain aur wo chahti hai ke (aakhon key ilaj key liye) uski aakhon mein surma lagaey (to kya ye jayez hai)? Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : (jahiliyat mein to) aurat saal pura guzarney par mengni phenka karti thi. (Islaamii shariyat mein to) ye iddat sirf chaar mahiney das din hai.
2085,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aurat key liye jayez nahin ke khawind key siwa kisi faut honey waley par teen din sey ziyada sog karey."
2086,"Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki zauja mohtarma (biwi) Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah aur aakhirat par eman rakhney wali kisi aurat key liye jayez nahin ke khawind key siwa kisi faut honey waley par teen din sey ziyada sog kerey."
2087,"Hazrat Umme Atiya (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aurat kisi faut honey waley par teen din sey ziyada sog na karey , magar biwi apney khawind par chaar mahiney das din sog kerey. (us doran mein) wo rangin kapda na pehney, magar kuchh safed kuchh rangin kapda pehan sakti hai, aur surma na lagaey h, aur khushbu na lagaey magar (maahwari sey farigh ho kar) ghusl key moqey par thodi si ood hindi ya azfaar khushbu istimal kar ley."
2088,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : merey nikah main eik aurat thi, mujhey wo pasand thi lekin abba jaan usey pasand nahin kartey they. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ye baat batai to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney mujhey hukm diya ke usey Talaq dey dun, chunanche mainey usey Talaq dey di."
2089,Hazrat abu-Abdur-Rehman (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ko uskey walid ya walida ney hukm diya ke apni biwi ko Talaq dey dey to usney sau ghulam azad karney ki nazar maan li (agar wo biwi ko Talaq dey to so ghulam azad kerega). wo Hazrat Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) key paas aaya to dekha ke wo zuhaa (chaasht) ki namaz padh rahey hain aur usey taweel (lambi) kartey jatey hain. (Zohar ki namaz key baad bhi) unhoney Zohar sey Asr tak (nafl) namaz ada ki. (aakhir jab moqey mila to) usney un sey masla poochha. Hazrat Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : apni nazar puri kar aur waliden ki farman-bardari kar. Hazrat Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey (ye farman) suna hai : baap jannat ka darmiyan wala darwaza hai. ab (tumhari marzi hai) apney waliden ka khayal rakho ya na rakho.
